{"tid":454411,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"呢種短片真係害撚死人，今次真係柒到仆街","createTime":"2017-11-01T05:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T06:33:30.000Z","uid":87937,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34c1af3173b0189b3aa18ce529107a5a5cfcbd7b","tid":454411,"uid":87937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/01/135710_2cbbd86b9a51cf0ac8a7be90716f61d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F01%2F135710_2cbbd86b9a51cf0ac8a7be90716f61d1.jpg&h=37aa6123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說啱啱喺自修室溫書<br />\n咁溫到攰想睇下facebook啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到條片就真係想試下tap on 0<br />\n<br />\n點知一開 仆你個街<br />\n個背景聲係淫叫聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔撚記得校靜音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個個都望過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實之前都遇過呢種短片<br />\n但見有朋友分享 又見溫到攰搵野玩下<br />\n哇屌個個都聽到啲淫叫聲即刻望過黎<br />\n我個心跳快撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 面又紅<br />\n比人指住笑 我即刻攞袋走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後唔去自修室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48da30efafbfb76e348f3ce532587cec5659f60d","tid":454411,"uid":87937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T06:03:32.000Z","msg":"有無人都試過中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef437eb35b571ae2e